query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(n pi it2) NoHashJoin(ci it2 n pi t mii) */ select min(n.name),
min(t.title)
from person_info AS pi
inner join name AS n
on n.id = pi.person_id AND pi.info ilike '%india%'
inner join info_type AS it2
on pi.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info ilike '%birth%'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.person_id = n.id
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id
inner join movie_info_idx AS mii
on t.id = mii.movie_id AND ( mii.info ilike '8%' OR mii.info ilike '9%' OR mii.info ilike '10%')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mii.info_type_id AND it1.info ilike 'rating';
